    $k_{pCln}$ & production rate Cln ($\text{min}^{-1}\cdot \text{mol}^{-1}$)& 0 & 1.606 \\ \hline
    $k_{R}$ & synthesis coefficient for internal biomass (arb.unit)& 4.089 & 1.04 \\ \hline
    $k_{Am}$ & synthesis coefficient for structural biomass of mother (arb.unit)& 1 & 0 \\ \hline
